---
title: Teriyaki-Sambal Chicken Donburi Bowl with Garlic Rice, Sugar Snaps and Pickled Carrot
description: A staple in Japanese cuisine, 'donburi' roughly translates as 'rice-bowl dish', hinting towards the comforting nature of this delicious dish.
